title: The Best Zac Efron Ab Moments From the New Baywatch Trailer
text:
Splash   Perhaps to make this almost-spring Wednesday a little more tolerable, Zac Efron shared a new Baywatch trailer on Twitter this morning. The two and a half minute teaser gives a little more detail about the plot, Efron's Ryan Lochte-esque character, and additionally shows a lot of Priyanka Chopra scheming and Dwayne Johnson running around shirtless. Got a new one for you this #BeBaywatch #May26 pic.twitter.com/ykF1vAk0wh 
— Zac Efron (@ZacEfron)   It's all nice, but the real showstoppers are Zefron's abs, which turn up five times. Here, all the ab-tastic moments: Twitter
